00:00:01.500 --> 00:00:02.860
FEMALE SPEAKER: I've been
a big fan of Art

00:00:02.860 --> 00:00:04.180
for many, many years.

00:00:04.180 --> 00:00:06.660
And a couple years ago, I
actually went to his studio in

00:00:06.660 --> 00:00:09.970
Seattle, Washington, and was
able to take a seminar, The

00:00:09.970 --> 00:00:11.430
Art of Composition.

00:00:11.430 --> 00:00:14.110
And it really helped change my
view of how I look through the

00:00:14.110 --> 00:00:15.310
viewfinder of the camera.

00:00:15.310 --> 00:00:17.220
And you're going to get a taste
of that today, which is

00:00:17.220 --> 00:00:19.020
