00:00:45.490 --> 00:00:46.440
Visit his website.

00:00:46.440 --> 00:00:47.940
You'll see.

00:00:47.940 --> 00:00:51.130
To sum it up, Art focuses on
what's beautiful on the earth.

00:00:51.130 --> 00:00:53.360
And it's my extreme pleasure
and honor to be able to

00:00:53.360 --> 00:00:56.072
