00:01:01.420 --> 00:01:06.220
ART WOLFE: Normally I roam the
audience, but speaking of the

00:01:06.220 --> 00:01:09.430
audience, I would just like a
show of hands of how many

00:01:09.430 --> 00:01:12.980
